---
layout: default
title: About
---

<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row lg:flex-row items-center justify-center text-md">
    {% if author.avatar %}
        <a href="{{ author.homepage | url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            <img class="w-32 h-32 md:w-40 md:h-40 m-5" src="{{ author.avatar | url }}" width="128" height="128" alt="Author avatar">
        </a>
    {% endif %}

    <div class="text-center mt-8">
        <h1 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 leading-relaxed mt-0 mb-1">
            <a href="{{ author.homepage | url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ author.name }}</a>
        </h1>
        {% if author.email %}
        <div class="text-gray-600">
            <a href="mailto:{{ author.email }}">{{ author.email }}</a>
        </div>
        {% endif %}
        {% if author.phone %}
        <div class="text-gray-600">
            <a href="tel:{{ author.phone }}">{{ author.phone }}</a>
        </div>
        {% endif %}
        {% if author.bio %}
        <p class="mt-3 text-gray-700">{{ author.bio }}</p>
        {% endif %}
    </div>
</div>
<div class="flex flex-col mt-10">
    <p class="text-md"> Hi, this is my personal blog sharing all sorts of information and ideas in regard to computer science, web development, free and open source computing, digital rights, etc. </p>
</div>

